text: Nursholeh (22 August 1957 - 23 August 2020) was an Indonesian politician. He was Mayor of Tegal between 2017 and 2019. He lost his re-election bid in 2018. He was born in Tegal, Central Java. He was a member of the Golkar Party. Nursholeh died on 23 August 2020, one day after his 63rd birthday in Tegal.Mantan Wali Kota Tegal M Nursholeh Wafat, Semasa Hidup Berjuluk Bapak Sastrawan Tegalan ==References== Category:1957 births Category:2020 deaths Category:Indonesian mayors
